title: (x) chubby font on Veer wallpaper - Sauna {David Bailey}
content:

[http://www.veer.com/download/wallpaper/relax800x600.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20070329121456/http:/www.veer.com/download/wallpaper/relax800x600.jpg)

author: dotrobert

comments.content:
[Sauna by Underware](http://web.archive.org/web/20070329121456/http:/www.underware.nl/site2/index.php3?id1=sauna&id2=overview)

Says it at the bottom, :-P
oh damn. i’m an idiot. Guess I was in a bit too much of a rush tonight.

We dearly try to credit all of the images and typefaces used on our [wallpaper](http://web.archive.org/web/20070329121456/http:/www.veer.com/ideas/wallpaper/) designs. Please let me know if your ever discover one that is missing. I’ll correct it, pronto.
